  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've probably automated factories on alien planets many times, but have you ever automated a settlement of alcoholic dwarves?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/8ea092fc68761638be4c3a0dd740feb8.poster.avif?t=1772970051\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/8ea092fc68761638be4c3a0dd740feb8.webm?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/8ea092fc68761638be4c3a0dd740feb8.mp4?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extract, create, process. And most of all - survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three game modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Story: Discover the fate of the dwarves and face various challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sandbox: Ground is for good fun without limits!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/d34524153bfbe3d94d435cc3ec545108.webp?t=1772970051\" width=208 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Did you know that you can make a bomb with magic powder and a pot? The fruit ground in the mill creates a puree - and hence the way to moonshine. There are so many things to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/5c8f3447c4da9136f587cbc46379f59b.poster.avif?t=1772970051\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/5c8f3447c4da9136f587cbc46379f59b.webm?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/5c8f3447c4da9136f587cbc46379f59b.mp4?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/83bf5d4b80af2fa6f9d8ffedbfe8b0f8.webp?t=1772970051\" width=135 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A close clash with a troll cannot end well, especially for small creatures such as dwarves. A tall structure called a tower comes to the rescue. You can drop almost anything on enemy heads.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you throw a stone? You can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you throw an axe? You can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you throw a goat? Of course you can! The question is - is it worth it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/9bbeaef91f74daa92a9489a827036724.poster.avif?t=1772970051\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/9bbeaef91f74daa92a9489a827036724.webm?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/9bbeaef91f74daa92a9489a827036724.mp4?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've probably automated factories on alien planets many times, but have you ever automated a settlement of alcoholic dwarves?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/8ea092fc68761638be4c3a0dd740feb8.poster.avif?t=1772970051\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/8ea092fc68761638be4c3a0dd740feb8.webm?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/8ea092fc68761638be4c3a0dd740feb8.mp4?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extract, create, process. And most of all - survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three game modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Story: Discover the fate of the dwarves and face various challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sandbox: Ground is for good fun without limits!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/d34524153bfbe3d94d435cc3ec545108.webp?t=1772970051\" width=208 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Did you know that you can make a bomb with magic powder and a pot? The fruit ground in the mill creates a puree - and hence the way to moonshine. There are so many things to discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/5c8f3447c4da9136f587cbc46379f59b.poster.avif?t=1772970051\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/5c8f3447c4da9136f587cbc46379f59b.webm?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/5c8f3447c4da9136f587cbc46379f59b.mp4?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/83bf5d4b80af2fa6f9d8ffedbfe8b0f8.webp?t=1772970051\" width=135 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A close clash with a troll cannot end well, especially for small creatures such as dwarves. A tall structure called a tower comes to the rescue. You can drop almost anything on enemy heads.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you throw a stone? You can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you throw an axe? You can.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you throw a goat? Of course you can! The question is - is it worth it.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/9bbeaef91f74daa92a9489a827036724.poster.avif?t=1772970051\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/9bbeaef91f74daa92a9489a827036724.webm?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2540060/extras/9bbeaef91f74daa92a9489a827036724.mp4?t=1772970051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
